A text search engine based on Whoosh (https://bitbucket.org/mchaput/whoosh/wiki/Home).

To play with it, create a virtualenv:
$ mkvirtualenv gitpoints-searcher
$ git clone <this repo>
$ cd playground/searcher
$ pip install -r requirements.txt

To run the tests (assuming $PWD == gitpoints/searcher)
$ python -m unittest
